rows.label: tlk4537015301_msg0001
rows.name:
It's clear that the ancient Nopon
possessed a high level of knowledge.

rows.label: tlk4537015301_msg0002
rows.name:
But looking at the Nopon of the modern
day, it is difficult to imagine them
leaving behind artifacts of this nature.

rows.label: tlk4537015301_msg0003
rows.name:
What could have happened
to change the Nopon race so
in the intervening years...?
